props.content:
 Butter, five cents;  
Balm Oil, five cents;  
 Grease, five cents;  
Verdigris, five cents;  


 mix together; or take ashes, lard, and anguish honey, of a like quantity, and make an ointment thereof by mixing.

Sulphur, five cents;
Balsam, five cents;
Magic balm, five cents.
Mithridat, five cents.
Blue finherb. water, five cents.

Mix these all together, and give at once to drink. Probatum. But this must be given while the cow is being milked.
